message.body: Hey! I know you have a busy weekend but Liz and Va and I are at the ICA and gonna get drinks after
Hey!! I just got home and got your text! Was out all night with julians family...so tired now!
Hope you guys are having fun!
I'm gonna smoke a cigarette and get in bed.
What are you doing tomorrow night?
Hey! Probably gonna make some curtains tonight. Leaving for Harrisburg in the AM.
Haha that's cool. I'm supposed to go to a party tonight, but not really feeling it...wanted to see if you were around!

Yeah we had fun! Drank beers at local 44 after
